</selectionEntry><selectionEntry id="85df-0ac0-130c-74cf" name="Softskin Transport" hidden="false" collective="false" import="true" type="upgrade">
  <profiles>
    <profile id="5663-3d17-b628-194c" name="Softskin Transport" typeId="5cbd-556d-67b5-1bd9" typeName="Command Card" hidden="false">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">This Infantry or Gun Unit may add a Softskin Transport Attachment. The number of vehicles in the Unit is as follows:Add one Softskin Transport for every six Infantry Teams in the Unit.Add one Softskin Transport for each Gun Team in the UnitThe characteristics of a Softskin Transport are shown of the back of this card.
MOTIVATIONCONFIDENT4+
SKILLGREEN5+
IS HIT ONAGGRESSIVE3+
SAVETANK5+
TACTICALTERRAIN DASHCROSS COUNTRY DASHROAD DASHCROSS-10&quot;/25cm12&quot;/30cm32&quot;/80cm4+SPECIAL RULESPassengers 6, Tractor: Team can carry six Infantry Teams or one Gun Team as Passengers.Softskin: If a Transport is Destroyed, any Passengers it is carrying are also Destroyed, and all Transports must be Sent to the Rear immediately. All Passengers must Dismount from this Unit at the same time. Empty Transport Teams must be Sent to the Rear.  
Unarmoured: Team cannot Charge into Contact and must Break Off if Assaulted.</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Notes" typeId="75a6-20ee-1c76-640a">US, Build, Unit (Infantry or Gun)</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile id="9568-900f-077e-8bca" name="Forces ID" typeId="86a9-a6ee-b9bd-dafe" typeName="Forces ID" hidden="false">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="ID" typeId="846f-94be-be15-4936">5b965f5a-1196-50bb-b28e-4d08b2fac954</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
  </profiles>
  <costs>
